  "texts": [
    "This is why this article should be seen more as an abstract guideline than a real blueprint for specific prompting commands.",
    "As you can see from our opening example, prompts or commands that worked yesterday may be obsolete tomorrow.",
    "However, if you understand the way these systems are created, you can anticipate and adapt changes at an early stage.",
    "In general, it is important to ask questions in as structured a way as possible and to use creative additions to steer the answers in the right direction.",
    "And not always accept the first answer that comes along."
